<D>__{sorry to disturb you, sir, but there's been some trouble next door. i'd like to ask you a few questions.}
<C>__{man}
<D>__{what happened?}
<C>__{shermin}
<D>__{there's a possibility that mrs. haydn's been kidnapped. we're hoping you might have seen something.}
